<li id="cite_note-7"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFHall.2C_S.H._and_Hall.2C_G.W._and_McCall.2C_J.A.2000">Hall, S.H. and Hall, G.W. and McCall, J.A. (2000). <i>High Speed Digital System Design: A Handbook of Interconnect Theory and Design Practices</i>. Wiley New York.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=High+Speed+Digital+System+Design%3A+A+Handbook+of+Interconnect+Theory+and+Design+Practices&amp;rft.aulast=Hall%2C+S.H.+and+Hall%2C+G.W.+and+McCall%2C+J.A.&amp;rft.au=Hall%2C+S.H.+and+Hall%2C+G.W.+and+McCall%2C+J.A.&amp;rft.date=2000&amp;rft.pub=Wiley+New+York&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Speed_of_light"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
