<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFY_Jack_Ng2004">Y Jack Ng (2004). <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=RntpN7OesBsC" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=RntpN7OesBsC" rel="nofollow">"Quantum Foam and Quantum Gravity Phenomenology"</a>. in Giovanni Amelino-Camelia &amp; Jerzy Kowalski-Glikman (editors). <i>Planck Scale Effects in Astrophysics and Cosmology</i>. Springer. pp.&#160;321<i>ff</i>. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/3540252630" class="internal">ISBN 3540252630</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=RntpN7OesBsC" class="external free" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=RntpN7OesBsC" rel="nofollow">http://books.google.com/books?id=RntpN7OesBsC</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Quantum+Foam+and+Quantum+Gravity+Phenomenology&amp;rft.atitle=Planck+Scale+Effects+in+Astrophysics+and+Cosmology&amp;rft.aulast=Y+Jack+Ng&amp;rft.au=Y+Jack+Ng&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B321%27%27ff%27%27&amp;rft.pub=Springer&amp;rft.isbn=3540252630&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DRntpN7OesBsC&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Speed_of_light"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
